Package: clearnightskynearme
Type: Package
Title: Clear sky night near the user
Version: 0.1.4
Author: Rishi Das Roy
Maintainer: Rishi Das Roy <rishi.dasroy@gmail.com>
Description: It finds clear sky night near the user defined location and area.
    At present the user can choose predefined cities and give a radius to search 
    clear sky night around the user.
